('68', 'Rimmel London 1000 Kisses Lip Liner - Cappuccino', '10', '4', 'Rimmel London 1000 Kisses Lip Liner is a good way to make your lips look more beautiful. It\'s a long-wear wood pencil, which you can comfortably wear up to 8 hours. Its soft, creamy surface slides precisely along the lips, without any pull or drag.', 170, 'n/a', 'http://192.168.1.173/webService/Images/68.jpg'),
